            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In hunc <note>sic</note> tomolo <expan><abbr>req</abbr><ex>ui</ex></expan><lb break="no" n="2"/>escit in pace bon<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <surplus>me</surplus>memo<lb break="no" n="3"/>ri<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> nom&amp;lt;i=E&amp;gt;ne Rignedrudis <lb n="4"/>cara parent&amp;lt;i=E&amp;gt;bus et ni<lb break="no" n="5"/>mium relicta amore <lb n="6"/>qui vixit in hunc <note>sic</note> <lb n="7"/>saecolo <note>sic</note> annos XIIIIII <lb n="8"/>et migravit de h&amp;lt;o=V&amp;gt;c mun<lb break="no" n="9"/>do XV K<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>l</abbr><ex>enda</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> Ma<surplus>d</surplus>ias 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Platte ist aus einem älteren, römischen Pilastergesims wiederverwendet.</p>
            </div>
